    <PrePause>-1</PrePause>
    <LockConversation>True</LockConversation>
    <IgnoreCarried>False</IgnoreCarried>
    <AllowNPCTrigger>False</AllowNPCTrigger>
    <SpeechStyle>Regular</SpeechStyle>
    <SpeechHue>-1</SpeechHue>
  </SpeechEntry>
  <SpeechEntry>
    <EntryNumber>80</EntryNumber>
    <ID>80</ID>
    <Text>My father was a dedicated shepherd, always putting the needs of his flock first. He taught me the importance of dedication. Do you believe in dedication?</Text>
    <Keywords>father</Keywords>
    <DependsOn>-1</DependsOn>
    <Pause>1</Pause>
    <PrePause>-1</PrePause>
    <LockConversation>True</LockConversation>
    <IgnoreCarried>False</IgnoreCarried>
    <AllowNPCTrigger>False</AllowNPCTrigger>
    <SpeechStyle>Regular</SpeechStyle>
    <SpeechHue>-1</SpeechHue>
  </SpeechEntry>
  <SpeechEntry>
    <EntryNumber>90</EntryNumber>
    <ID>90</ID>
    <Text>The meadows here are lush and green, providing the perfect food for the sheep. It's a blessing to have such land. Do you appreciate nature's blessings?</Text>
    <Keywords>meadows</Keywords>
    <DependsOn>-1</DependsOn>
    <Pause>1</Pause>
    <PrePause>-1</PrePause>
    <LockConversation>True</LockConversation>
