    <AllowNPCTrigger>False</AllowNPCTrigger>
    <SpeechStyle>Regular</SpeechStyle>
    <SpeechHue>-1</SpeechHue>
  </SpeechEntry>
  <SpeechEntry>
    <EntryNumber>100</EntryNumber>
    <ID>100</ID>
    <Text>Ah, the tales of the legendary sheep speak of a special sheep with golden fleece. It's said that whoever finds it will be granted a reward. Are you seeking rewards?</Text>
