  <SpeechEntry>
    <EntryNumber>110</EntryNumber>
    <ID>110</ID>
    <Text>Rewards come in many forms, not just gold or treasures. Sometimes, the reward is the journey itself. But for you, kind traveler, I have a small token of appreciation for your interest. Here, take this.</Text>
